text: Elżbieta Jankowska (born 2 October 1964) is a Polish rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kożuchów
